     ## Fix[0m[2m approach[0m[2m
     
     The clean[0m[2mest approach: add[0m[2m an atomic[0m[2m `try[0m[2m_de[0m[2mcrement` method[0m[2m to `Inventory[0m[2m` that checks[0m[2m and decre[0m[2mments in[0m[2m one[0m[2m async[0m[2m operation ([0m[2mno yield[0m[2m point between check[0m[2m and decre[0m[2mment),[0m[2m and re[0m[2morder the[0m[2m checkout flow to[0m[2m:[0m[2m
     
